<br>
As it stands, EQ obviously uses a static list of gear and just references to it are stored in your character. However an extra byte of info on the *character*'s data (alongside the value that holds the instance of the item, or part of it) wouldnt be too rediculous. They added more than that for AA advancement...<br>
